          "html": "<div style=\"padding:24px\"><div style=\"color:#f0883e;font-size:32px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px\">PlantPAx Template Library</div><div style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:24px\">188 Vision templates and 13 windows from <a href=\"https://github.com/teslasolar/Flintium\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#58a6ff\">teslasolar/Flintium</a>, organised by category. Click a chip to open that gallery; each card links back to the source on GitHub.</div><div style=\"margin-bottom:16px\"><div style=\"color:#e6edf3;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px\">Templates</div><a href=\"#view=Flintium/Templates/Templates_All\" style=\"display:inline-block;margin:4px 8px 4px 0;padding:8px 14px;background:#161b22;border:1px solid #2a313c;border-radius:6px;color:#58a6ff;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px\">All (188)</a><a href=\"#view=Flintium/Templates/Templates_Components\" style=\"display:inline-block;margin:4px 8px 4px 0;padding:8px 14px;background:#161b22;border:1px solid #2a313c;border-radius:6px;color:#58a6ff;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px\">Components (38)</a><a href=\"#view=Flintium/Templates/Templates_DisplayObjects\" style=\"display:inline-block;margin:4px 8px 4px 0;padding:8px 14px;background:#161b22;border:1px solid #2a313c;border-radius:6px;color:#58a6ff;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px\">DisplayObjects (7)</a><a href=\"#view=Flintium/Templates/Templates_Icons\" style=\"display:inline-block;margin:4px 8px 4px 0;padding:8px 14px;background:#161b22;border:1px solid #2a313c;border-radius:6px;color:#58a6ff;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px\">Icons (97)</a><a href=\"#view=Flintium/Templates/Templates_Panels\" style=\"display:inline-block;margin:4px 8px 4px 0;padding:8px 14px;background:#161b22;border:1px solid #2a313c;border-radius:6px;color:#58a6ff;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px\">Panels (46)</a></div><div style=\"margin-bottom:16px\"><div style=\"color:#e6edf3;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px\">Wi